00:51:44.620 --> 00:51:46.828 align:middle line:10%
All of these plants.

00:51:46.828 --> 00:51:55.160 align:middle line:84%
I see these plants selecting
their caretakers, the teachers.

00:51:55.160 --> 00:51:58.900 align:middle line:84%
In my opinion, we're
caretakers of the earth.

00:51:58.900 --> 00:51:59.500 align:middle line:90%
They need us.

00:51:59.500 --> 00:52:04.770 align:middle line:90%


