bags inside and take

00:52:38.180 --> 00:52:40.870 align:middle line:90%
stock of our surroundings.

00:52:40.870 --> 00:52:43.730 align:middle line:84%
Past the living room, with
its skins and trappings,

00:52:43.730 --> 00:52:46.900 align:middle line:84%
