in the dining room, which

00:52:46.900 --> 00:52:48.950 align:middle line:84%
doubles as an altar
space when Ron

00:52:48.950 --> 00:52:51.920 align:middle line:90%
conducts ayahuasca ceremonies.

00:52:51.920 --> 00:52:53.820 align:middle line:84%
The ayahuasca is
boiling in a big,

