psychedelic effects,

00:53:26.130 --> 00:53:30.170 align:middle line:84%
5-MeO-DMT is not
illegal at this time.

00:53:30.170 --> 00:53:31.730 align:middle line:84%
That may be because
the chemical is

00:53:31.730 --> 00:53:35.140 align:middle line:84%
native to the brain in both
