his castle for a thatched hut,

00:54:08.610 --> 00:54:12.120 align:middle line:84%
and his lab coat for
Bermuda shorts and beads.

00:54:12.120 --> 00:54:16.170 align:middle line:84%
Dr. Juan reads the brain
waves, and shaman Ron

