00:54:21.890 --> 00:54:25.410 align:middle line:84%
into the deep reaches of
inner space, like a tag team

00:54:25.410 --> 00:54:30.320 align:middle line:84%
the unites the modern with the
archaic, science and shamanism.

00:54:30.320 --> 00:54:31.520 align:middle line:90%
So sure.

