It's all in the name
of science, after all.

00:54:37.290 --> 00:54:43.440 align:middle line:90%


00:54:43.440 --> 00:54:45.840 align:middle line:84%
There's something
curious about DMT

00:54:45.840 --> 00:54:47.980 align:middle line:84%
and all its analogs
which are found

00:54:47.980 --> 00:54:50.110 align:middle line:84%
throughout many of
nature's creatures,

00:54:50.110 --> 00:54:54.500 align:middle line:84%
in a swath of plants
and toads species.

00:54:54.500 --> 00:54:58.680 align:middle line:84%
Renowned psychedelic chemist,
Alexander Sasha Shulgin,

00:54:58.680 --> 00:55:01.135 align:middle line:84%
claims in his book,
"Tihkal, Tryptamines

00:55:01.135 --> 00:55:06.490 align:middle line:84%
