"DMT is in this flower here,

00:55:06.490 --> 00:55:09.730 align:middle line:84%
in that tree over there,
and in yonder animal.

00:55:09.730 --> 00:55:16.110 align:middle line:84%
It is most simply, almost
everywhere you choose to look."

