01:17:39.320 --> 01:17:41.940 align:middle line:90%


01:17:41.940 --> 01:17:42.907 align:middle line:90%
Different effect.

01:17:42.907 --> 01:17:45.490 align:middle line:84%
But ultimately, if you're seeing
energy, you're seeing energy,

01:17:45.490 --> 01:17:46.570 align:middle line:90%
you know?

01:17:46.570 --> 01:17:49.910 align:middle line:84%
Whether it's in a dream, with a
plant, or with nothing at all.

01:17:49.910 --> 01:17:51.780 align:middle line:84%
Here in the Andean
system, if you

01:17:51.780 --> 01:17:55.730 align:middle line:84%
talk to the caros, the keepers
of the sacred knowledge,

01:17:55.730 --> 01:17:59.400 align:middle line:84%
they don't traditionally
used San Pedro, ayahuasca,

01:17:59.400 --> 01:18:01.250 align:middle line:90%
or other plants.

01:18:01.250 --> 01:18:05.540 align:middle line:84%
The system that they use is
they see energy without it.

01:18:05.540 --> 01:18:08.695 align:middle line:90%


01:18:08.695 --> 01:18:11.600 align:middle line:84%
>>They were said to have
lived in the highlands of Peru

01:18:11.600 --> 01:18:13.650 align:middle line:90%
for thousands of years.

01:18:13.650 --> 01:18:17.210 align:middle line:84%
And they hadn't been defeated
by the pre-Incas, the Incas,

01:18:17.210 --> 01:18:21.350 align:middle line:84%
or the conquistadors, so
their culture was intact.

01:18:21.350 --> 01:18:22.520 align:middle line:90%
It was funny.

01:18:22.520 --> 01:18:24.500 align:middle line:84%
My journey had led
me all this way

01:18:24.500 --> 01:18:26.830 align:middle line:84%
up a sacred mountain
to remind me

01:18:26.830 --> 01:18:30.885 align:middle line:84%
that the finger that points at
the sun is not the sun itself.

01:18:30.885 --> 01:18:34.700 align:middle line:84%
Ayahuasca, all the shamanic
accoutrements, all those

01:18:34.700 --> 01:18:37.060 align:middle line:90%
were powerful allies, indeed.

01:18:37.060 --> 01:18:39.160 align:middle line:84%
But they were just
activating what we all

01:18:39.160 --> 01:18:41.510 align:middle line:90%
have inside us all along.

01:18:41.510 --> 01:18:45.000 align:middle line:84%
The innate ability
to see and connect

01:18:45.000 --> 01:18:47.035 align:middle line:84%
with the energetic
grids of the universe.

01:18:47.035 --> 01:18:49.900 align:middle line:90%


01:18:49.900 --> 01:18:54.490 align:middle line:84%
