01:18:54.490 --> 01:18:56.760 align:middle line:90%
It's everywhere, isn't it?

01:18:56.760 --> 01:18:59.440 align:middle line:84%
It's the energy of the
planet, and the stars,

01:18:59.440 --> 01:19:01.503 align:middle line:90%
and the infinite.

01:19:01.503 --> 01:19:05.751 align:middle line:84%
Right, Kevin says,
smiling at me warmly

01:19:05.751 --> 01:19:08.520 align:middle line:90%
while he smokes his mapacho.

01:19:08.520 --> 01:19:13.630 align:middle line:84%
The Inca's call it Kausay
Pacha, the energy universe,

01:19:13.630 --> 01:19:15.250 align:middle line:90%
he tells us.

01:19:15.250 --> 01:19:18.610 align:middle line:84%
It's the ability to perceive
this invisible world that

01:19:18.610 --> 01:19:21.280 align:middle line:84%
means your heart chakra
and your third eye

01:19:21.280 --> 01:19:25.850 align:middle line:84%
are connected on
an energetic level.

01:19:25.850 --> 01:19:28.110 align:middle line:84%
And with that, we
continue our climb.

01:19:28.110 --> 01:19:36.720 align:middle line:90%


01:19:36.720 --> 01:19:38.900 align:middle line:84%
A few hundred meters
up on the left

01:19:38.900 --> 01:19:41.530 align:middle line:84%
