the edge of a bluff.

01:19:41.530 --> 01:19:43.970 align:middle line:84%
A little ruined fort,
balanced precariously

01:19:43.970 --> 01:19:45.820 align:middle line:90%
on the edge of the abyss.

01:19:45.820 --> 01:19:49.930 align:middle line:84%
Directly above,
Viracocha's stony head.

01:19:49.930 --> 01:19:52.110 align:middle line:84%
