the endless free-fall

01:19:52.110 --> 01:19:53.473 align:middle line:90%
of the valley blood.

01:19:53.473 --> 01:19:56.311 align:middle line:90%


01:19:56.311 --> 01:20:01.050 align:middle line:84%
Ollantaytambo spreads itself
out beneath us like a lover.

01:20:01.050 --> 01:20:04.310 align:middle line:84%
The rolling fields
unfolding one into another,

01:20:04.310 --> 01:20:07.020 align:middle line:90%
hugged by mountains.

01:20:07.020 --> 01:20:10.700 align:middle line:84%
I understand, then, what
the Incas must have felt.

01:20:10.700 --> 01:20:13.490 align:middle line:84%
The living presence
of the Earth itself,

01:20:13.490 --> 01:20:16.820 align:middle line:90%
which they call Pachamama.

01:20:16.820 --> 01:20:19.990 align:middle line:84%
The more I tuned into it,
the more spatially aware

01:20:19.990 --> 01:20:23.900 align:middle line:84%
I became of the open landscape
as a living organism,

01:20:23.900 --> 01:20:29.870 align:middle line:84%
connected to the clouds and sky,
and up into the heavens above.

01:20:29.870 --> 01:20:32.798 align:middle line:90%
[FLUTE MUSIC]

01:20:32.798 --> 01:20:35.240 align:middle line:90%


01:20:35.240 --> 01:20:37.650 align:middle line:84%
The caro's prophecies
specifically

01:20:37.650 --> 01:20:42.800 align:middle line:84%
