which the world will

01:20:45.880 --> 01:20:49.550 align:middle line:84%
be turned right side up,
and harmony and order

01:20:49.550 --> 01:20:51.970 align:middle line:90%
will be restored.

01:20:51.970 --> 01:20:55.180 align:middle line:84%
According to the caros,
the last Pachacuti

01:20:55.180 --> 01:20:58.880 align:middle line:84%
