empire, breaking

01:21:01.330 --> 01:21:04.350 align:middle line:84%
the celestial connection
woven across the land,

01:21:04.350 --> 01:21:08.830 align:middle line:84%
in the temples and
shrines, and chaos reigned.

01:21:08.830 --> 01:21:12.186 align:middle line:84%
Patiently, the caros
have waited for the time

01:21:12.186 --> 01:21:13.310 align:middle line:90%
their prophecies predicted.

01:21:13.310 --> 01:21:16.600 align:middle line:90%


01:21:16.600 --> 01:21:18.650 align:middle line:84%
>>In the past, a
shaman would be living

01:21:18.650 --> 01:21:21.610 align:middle line:84%
