we're on a world scale.

01:21:36.546 --> 01:21:39.210 align:middle line:84%
So it's not just about
individual evolution.

01:21:39.210 --> 01:21:42.200 align:middle line:84%
It's about a
planetary evolution.

01:21:42.200 --> 01:21:45.980 align:middle line:84%
When we work together
in cooperative molds,

01:21:45.980 --> 01:21:50.030 align:middle line:84%
we can change the
dream of this planet.

01:21:50.030 --> 01:21:54.350 align:middle line:84%
>>That's why we've all been
drawn here, Kevin says, sagely.

01:21:54.350 --> 01:21:58.620 align:middle line:84%
Our energy bodies are awakening
to a deeper understanding

01:21:58.620 --> 01:22:02.460 align:middle line:90%
of the true nature of reality.

01:22:02.460 --> 01:22:07.520 align:middle line:84%
Down there, Kevin says, pointing
towards civilization below us,

01:22:07.520 --> 01:22:09.880 align:middle line:84%
with a grand sweep
of his hand, we're

01:22:09.880 --> 01:22:12.360 align:middle line:90%
in normal physical reality.

01:22:12.360 --> 01:22:14.970 align:middle line:84%
We have filters that
adjust our perception.

01:22:14.970 --> 01:22:17.390 align:middle line:10%
And this is why every
culture in the world

01:22:17.390 --> 01:22:21.050 align:middle line:10%
has different views
on how reality is.

01:22:21.050 --> 01:22:24.410 align:middle line:84%
The path of shamanism is
like climbing this mountain,

01:22:24.410 --> 01:22:27.090 align:middle line:90%
he continues.

01:22:27.090 --> 01:22:31.040 align:middle line:84%
This world is a school, but
life's not just about learning.

01:22:31.040 --> 01:22:33.590 align:middle line:90%
It's about remembering.

01:22:33.590 --> 01:22:36.040 align:middle line:90%
At one time, we knew everything.

01:22:36.040 --> 01:22:41.000 align:middle line:84%
But when we come down here,
they blank out your memory.

01:22:41.000 --> 01:22:44.870 align:middle line:84%
When you take the filters off,
with tools like ayahuasca,

01:22:44.870 --> 01:22:48.660 align:middle line:84%
you see the greater
reality, he continues.

01:22:48.660 --> 01:22:51.455 align:middle line:90%
The key is to remember.

01:22:51.455 --> 01:22:53.529 align:middle line:90%
Remember.

01:22:53.529 --> 01:22:54.028 align:middle line:90%
Remember.

01:22:54.028 --> 01:22:57.730 align:middle line:90%


01:22:57.730 --> 01:22:59.860 align:middle line:90%
And I do.

01:22:59.860 --> 01:23:04.800 align:middle line:84%
Beneath the flesh is a spiritual
body that comes, like the Inca,

01:23:04.800 --> 01:23:06.340 align:middle line:90%
from the sun.

01:23:06.340 --> 01:23:09.180 align:middle line:84%
But not the sun up
there in the sky.

01:23:09.180 --> 01:23:12.190 align:middle line:84%
There's another sun
that lies within,

01:23:12.190 --> 01:23:16.450 align:middle line:84%
and it burns with the
fire of a spiritual light.

01:23:16.450 --> 01:23:20.590 align:middle line:84%
Our souls are like emanations
from this central source.

01:23:20.590 --> 01:23:25.270 align:middle line:84%
It's where we come from,
and where we go back to.

01:23:25.270 --> 01:23:30.490 align:middle line:84%
Andean prophecy foretells of
the Taripaypacha or encounter

01:23:30.490 --> 01:23:32.730 align:middle line:90%
with the universe, he says.

01:23:32.730 --> 01:23:36.820 align:middle line:84%
It refers to a new golden
era in the human experience.

01:23:36.820 --> 01:23:41.840 align:middle line:10%
The age of meeting
ourselves again.

01:23:41.840 --> 01:23:46.190 align:middle line:10%
And then, through the gateway
of Viracocha's crown, far off

01:23:46.190 --> 01:23:49.660 align:middle line:10%
in the sky, I
suddenly spy two birds

01:23:49.660 --> 01:23:52.380 align:middle line:10%
sailing through a sea of blue.

01:23:52.380 --> 01:23:54.230 align:middle line:90%
Two eagles, perhaps.

01:23:54.230 --> 01:23:55.240 align:middle line:90%
Condors.

01:23:55.240 --> 01:23:56.480 align:middle line:90%
Or both.

01:23:56.480 --> 01:23:58.390 align:middle line:90%
They're too far away to tell.

01:23:58.390 --> 01:24:02.630 align:middle line:84%
But either way, I can
read the omen clearly.

01:24:02.630 --> 01:24:05.870 align:middle line:84%
The time of the
prophecies is upon us.

01:24:05.870 --> 01:24:10.340 align:middle line:84%
These are the times, indeed,
when all the binaries converge.

01:24:10.340 --> 01:24:12.900 align:middle line:84%
North and south,
eagle and condor,

01:24:12.900 --> 01:24:17.250 align:middle line:84%
old world and new, heaven
and earth, past and future.

01:24:17.250 --> 01:24:19.730 align:middle line:90%
And we are all part of it.

01:24:19.730 --> 01:24:22.200 align:middle line:84%
All part of the
universal awakening.

